Silence::

"Uh, no, I don't believe I've been formally introduced to him. But,
well, he sounds...eh, nice."  The uneasiness was profound in her
voice.  She felt uncomfortable because her protocol programs were
starting to fail her and she was fighting her urges to fight someone
of the opposite side. However, her promise to Rodimus stopped that
action, she still felt the need to fight or go flight with these bots
around. 

"Uhm, so anyway,"  she turned to Rodimus, "Perhaps you could give me
my assignment sir?"
